Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.14,0:03:19.43,Default_I,,0,0,0,,﻿A dream?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:23.31,0:03:24.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Dammit! Fucking shark!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:24.90,0:03:26.48,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Why'd he have to show up when\N﻿things were getting good!?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.48,0:03:29.27,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Moron. Moron.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:33.07,0:03:33.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Good morning.
