Dialogue: 0,0:03:39.16,0:03:40.91,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Shut the fuck up. It's morning!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:42.33,0:03:44.71,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Sorry about that. I'm just grumpy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.71,0:03:45.33,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿So?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:45.67,0:03:47.50,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This is the script for the next project!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:48.92,0:03:50.75,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿A script, huh.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:51.63,0:03:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,Chief, what's wrong?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.47,0:03:55.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Koganei, we're putting the\N﻿next project on hold.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:56.18,0:03:57.43,Default,,0,0,0,,"﻿On hold"?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.10,0:04:03.48,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I wonder if bunnies on the\N﻿mountain taste good.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.06,0:04:05.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But why are we putting it on-
Dialogue: 0,0:04:05.65,0:04:07.35,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We've got no money! No money!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:07.94,0:04:09.36,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿N-No way.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:09.36,0:04:11.36,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But didn't we make a huge\N﻿profit on the last one?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:11.74,0:04:14.65,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿All the profits went to paying off our debt.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:12.02,0:04:14.44,Sign _2,,0,0,0,,{\fad(400,200)\pos(203,349)}Apollo Productions Director:\NWakaba Miwa
Dialogue: 0,0:04:14.65,0:04:17.28,Default,,0,0,0,,So how are we gonna move on now?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.28,0:04:19.41,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We're discussing that right now!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:19.41,0:04:20.91,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Keep your shirt on.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.54,0:04:24.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Guess I wasted an all-night writing session.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.63,0:04:33.42,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Junpei, looks like you'd better think\N﻿of an alternative source of income.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.42,0:04:35.72,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿That's a bit harsh, even for you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:36.63,0:04:37.47,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿ ﻿Good morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.47,0:04:38.89,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hey, guys!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.76,0:04:43.93,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Sir? Sir, please use this.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.56,0:04:49.36,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿There's not much in there, but use all of it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.44,0:04:53.48,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Awesome. Kick ass!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.49,0:04:54.99,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿At least I wish it were that simple.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.99,0:04:56.28,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But I don't want it.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.20,0:04:59.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Sir!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.03,0:05:01.41,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Miwa, I appreciate the gesture, but no thanks.
