Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.79,0:05:07.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Apollo Productions won't go under so easily.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.04,0:05:10.25,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But do you have funding for the next project?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.25,0:05:11.00,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We do.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:11.00,0:05:11.88,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:12.00,0:05:14.21,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Everyone, gather round!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:14.84,0:05:19.84,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Friends. As you're well aware,\N﻿Apollo Productions is facing a crisis.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.84,0:05:23.68,Default,,0,0,0,,In order to overcome this crisis,\N﻿I'm going to need your help. ﻿
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.27,0:05:25.93,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Our help? What sort of help?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.56,0:05:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I need all of you to get side\N﻿jobs to provide funding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.42,0:05:32.46,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Side jobs?
