Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.53,0:06:24.41,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Have a drink.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.09,0:06:36.25,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.92,0:06:37.84,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿So sexy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:44.18,0:06:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Go! Go!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.48,0:06:56.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's not much.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:56.90,0:06:57.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Thanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.03,0:07:03.53,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Whoa, stop it! I'm getting too excited!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:06.66,0:07:07.53,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Like this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:09.75,0:07:11.96,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You really are a funny boy.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:12.58,0:07:15.29,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm Koganei Junpei.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.00,0:07:20.05,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Miss, you're the actress Mina\N﻿Yoshiko, aren't you?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.72,0:07:24.84,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Lucky!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:27.39,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I've seen all of your movies!
Dialogue: 0,0:07:27.39,0:07:29.72,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I had no idea college students liked my films.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.72,0:07:31.18,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm flattered.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:31.18,0:07:32.60,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm not in college.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.60,0:07:35.06,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm training to be a film director.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.06,0:07:36.65,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You're a director-hopeful?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.27,0:07:38.65,Default,,0,0,0,,I like you.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:38.65,0:07:39.57,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Want to dance?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.38,0:07:59.00,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Working at a host club to raise money.\N ﻿Look what we've stooped to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:59.00,0:08:00.38,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm satisfied.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:00.38,0:08:02.76,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Because you got to meet Mina Yoshiko?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.76,0:08:04.88,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Bingo! Correct!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.88,0:08:05.88,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Woo-hoo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:06.05,0:08:07.76,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿ ﻿I got her autographed handkerchief\N﻿and business card.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.18,0:08:11.22,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿And she also says she'll introduce\N﻿me to her film industry friends.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.22,0:08:11.97,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.98,0:08:12.85,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿She was just being polite.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:12.85,0:08:14.35,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Chief, pull yourself together!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:14.35,0:08:18.06,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I know you're trying to earn money,\N﻿but you don't need to be so reckless.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.06,0:08:20.44,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You think I can do this sort\N﻿of degrading thing sober?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.82,0:08:26.45,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No matter what, Apollo won't be crushed.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:26.45,0:08:28.62,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿But for my precious company...
