Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.94,0:35:23.77,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Shut up!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:26.65,0:35:28.19,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What are you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.19,0:35:28.98,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Stop it!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:28.99,0:35:29.69,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Stop struggling!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:33.20,0:35:33.78,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿No!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:35.46,0:35:36.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Stop-
Dialogue: 0,0:35:39.50,0:35:41.62,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿F-Feels nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.05,0:35:51.92,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Oh, crap!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.93,0:35:53.59,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Wh-What the fuck?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:53.59,0:35:55.01,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This nice?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:55.01,0:35:56.43,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You fucking grandma!
Dialogue: 0,0:35:56.43,0:35:58.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Let go! Leggo my dick!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.52,0:36:10.03,Default,,0,0,0,,S-Stop it, bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.11,0:36:12.19,Default,,0,0,0,,How is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:15.07,0:36:17.53,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Go, go, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:18.37,0:36:21.04,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿This is the way you scare people!
Dialogue: 0,0:36:44.89,0:36:46.60,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Well?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:47.65,0:36:49.90,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿You like it?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.66,0:37:04.37,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿To save my beloved daughter, I'd even\N﻿become a vampire if I had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:04.37,0:37:05.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:06.04,0:37:07.29,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:07.29,0:37:08.42,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Mom!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.42,0:37:09.67,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hitomi!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:14.92,0:37:15.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Cut!
Dialogue: 0,0:37:17.39,0:37:21.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Thanks to Miwa and the staff at Apollo\N﻿Productions, we finished filming.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:21.93,0:37:24.81,Default,,0,0,0,,It will be released around New Years.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:24.81,0:37:30.19,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Even though Miwa took over from Shibuya\N﻿as the director, it was a big hit.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.19,0:37:33.15,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Shoko was able to climb the wall to stardom.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:33.15,0:37:34.94,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Everything turned out well.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:39.45,0:37:40.53,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Congratulations.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.53,0:37:41.28,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Well then,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:41.28,0:37:44.66,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿it's about time for Apollo Productions to\N﻿make its first major motion picture.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.08,0:37:47.91,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿With Mina Yoshiko as a supporting actress.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:47.92,0:37:49.50,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Thank you, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.50,0:37:53.13,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Our film was number one at\N﻿the box office on New Years.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:53.13,0:37:56.47,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Thanks to that, Mikami Shoko's\N﻿popularity has risen dramatically.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:56.47,0:37:59.63,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Hopefully we can repay Shoko with this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:00.51,0:38:03.72,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿The truth is, Shoko is my\N﻿daughter with Shibuya.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.35,0:38:09.73,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿We divorced when she was in grade\N﻿school, so we sent her away.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:09.73,0:38:11.44,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿So that's what it is!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.44,0:38:14.07,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Good thing nothing happened between\N﻿you two after all, Junpei-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:15.15,0:38:20.49,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'm going to quit acting after\N﻿this and become a producer.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:20.49,0:38:21.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I hope to work with you again in the future.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:21.70,0:38:22.45,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿She's retiring?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.45,0:38:23.70,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What a waste!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:24.49,0:38:28.25,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿So the shadow-helper of Apollo\N﻿Productions is Mikami Shoko, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:28.25,0:38:29.66,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Guess so.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:29.67,0:38:31.75,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿And my knight in shining armor is Junpei-kun.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:31.75,0:38:32.67,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Just kidding!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:51.10,0:38:53.19,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿It's so cold and refreshing!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:53.19,0:38:54.73,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Miwa-san, you're showing me\N﻿how you really feel!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:55.57,0:38:57.11,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Come on, let's race!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:57.11,0:38:58.11,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Miwa-san!
Dialogue: 0,0:38:59.65,0:39:03.12,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿I'll always be with you!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:03.12,0:39:05.24,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿What? You'll always be what?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:06.33,0:39:08.16,Default,,0,0,0,,I can be so cheesy sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:13.25,0:39:16.92,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿Jeez! Where are you hiding?
Dialogue: 0,0:39:19.13,0:39:20.34,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿And so...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:20.34,0:39:22.93,Default,,0,0,0,,﻿my second adventure was also a crazy circus!
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.71,0:39:31.83,Default,,0,0,0,,And with that, everyone... have a nice day!
